data.description:
Welcome to this stunning 3 bed, 3.5 bath home situated on a large corner lot. Step inside to find a spacious, inviting floor plan that seamlessly blends comfort & style. The main level showcases a beautifully designed living area with an abundance of natural light, 
a gourmet kitchen boasts modern appliances, cabinet space, & large center island. Off the kitchen, you'll discover a charming dining area.  
On the main level, you'll find a luxurious primary suite, providing a peaceful oasis. Equipped with a spa-like ensuite bathroom,  a soaking tub, a separate shower, and his and her bathrooms,  this space is designed for ultimate relaxation. Upstairs, two additional spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom.
Beyond the main residence, an inground pool invites you to enjoy endless summer days basking in the sun or taking refreshing swims. The pool house is an incredible bonus, offering a full bathroom, a bar area, murphy bed, and a living room. An attached basement provides ample storage.
